定义中国商业力量。
Defining China's commercial power.
作者：冯超来源：商业人物（ID：biz-leaders）壹中国人知道了一种病毒，也知道了一个发布数据，名为“卫生健康委员会”的机构。
Author: Feng Chaoyuan: A Chinese know about a virus and a body that publishes data called the "Health and Wellness Commission."
该机构简称就是卫健委。
This body abbreviates is Wei Jianshi committee.
各级的卫生健康委员会是从各级卫生计生委（局）改名而来。
The Health Boards at all levels have been renamed from the Health and Family Health Boards (HFSCs) at all levels.
新名字添加了“健康”二字，改名是从上至下，从2018年3月，持续到2019年的春天。
The name "Health" was added, and the name was changed from top to bottom, from March 2018 to spring 2019.
一个省会城市的卫健委，是副省级城市卫健委，武汉卫健委属于此列。
The health committee of a provincial capital city is the vice-provincial city health committee, Wuhan health committee belongs to this category.
武汉市卫健委官方网站罗列了市卫健委的十六条职能。
The official website of Wuhan Health Committee lists 16 functions of the municipal health committee.
第三条：制定并落实全市疾病预防控制规划以及严重危害人民健康公共卫生问题的干预措施，组织实施免疫规划，组织开展传染病监测。
Article 3: Formulate and implement city-wide disease prevention and control plans and interventions that seriously endanger people's health and public health problems, organize immunization programs and organize and carry out infectious disease surveillance.
负责卫生应急工作，组织指导突发公共卫生事件的预防控制和各类突发公共事件的医疗卫生救援。
Responsible for health emergency work, organize and direct the prevention and control of public health emergencies and medical and health relief for public emergencies.
有两条职责是这样的：在武汉卫健委网站上，有政务公开相关消息。
There are two duties: in Wuhan Weijian Wei Commission website, there are government affairs related information.
网站刊发了《市卫生健康委2019年政府信息公开工作年度报告》。
The website published the 2019 Annual Report of the Municipal Health Commission on Government Information Disclosure.
报告第五部分提到“信息公开工作存在的问题”，“一是有效主动公开工作力度有待进一步加强。
The fifth part of the report refers to the "problems existing in the information disclosure work."
站在工作角度主动公开信息和公众热切关注想要知晓信息间还存在一定差距，需多站在公众角度公开与公众密切相关的信息”。
There is still a gap between self-disclosure and the public's eagerness to get to know the information. We need to be more open to the public in public. "
贰据武汉市纪委监察委消息，2016年7月21日，派驻武汉市卫计委（卫计委后更名为卫健委）纪检组正式成立。
Second, on July 21, 2016, the disciplinary inspection team accredited to the Wuhan Municipal Commission for Physical Planning (after the name of the Health and Physical Fitness Commission) was formally established, according to the disciplinary committee.
2017年年底，纪委发表《派驻市卫计委纪检组：我们这一年》一文。
At the end of 2017, the discipline inspection team accredited to the CPPCC: Our Year was published.
文章中称，“进驻一年来，纪检组共收到信访举报件219件，已办结196件，办结率90%。
"In the past year, the discipline inspection team has received 219 complaints and closed 196 complaints, a 90 percent closure rate," it said
立案30件，涉及处级干部3人，科级及以下27人，给予党纪政纪处分30人，其中移送司法12人”，“一年来，委领导班子开展廉政谈话480人次，进行提醒谈话和批评教育96人次”。
Thirty cases were registered, involving 3 cadres at the branch level and 27 below, and 30 disciplinary actions were taken against the Party, 12 of which were referred to the judiciary.
2017年4月，纪检组对2016年度全市党风廉政责任制考核排名靠后的市红十字会党组书记、专职副会长陈耘进行了工作约谈。
In April 2017, the Disciplinary Investigation Team conducted a job interview with Chen Pu, secretary and full-time vice-president of the Municipal Red Cross Society, who ranked second in the 2016 assessment of the city's integrity responsibility system.
纪委在一篇名为《派驻市卫计委纪检组：约谈党风廉政责任制考核排名靠后单位“一把手”》的文章里写道——“约谈指出了市红十字会在党风廉政建设中存在的廉政教育不深入，廉政制度不健全，主要领导主体责任意识淡薄等问题。
"The interview pointed out that the city Red Cross did not have in-depth integrity education, the integrity system was not perfect, and the main leader's sense of responsibility was weak.
约谈要求：要高度重视，提高认识”，“要吸取教训，深刻反思，深挖细查廉政教育、作风建设等方面存在的问题，建立健全有效管用的长效机制，促进干部干净干事，奋发有为”。
Interview requirements: to attach great importance to awareness-raising, "" to learn lessons, deep reflection, dig deep into integrity education, style building and other issues, establish a sound and effective long-term mechanism for effective management, promote clean cadres, and make great efforts.
2018年，纪检组编写了《武汉市卫生计生系统违法违纪典型案例警示录》（以下简称《警示录》）。
In 2018, the Disciplinary Investigation Team compiled a "typical case of violations of the health and family planning system in Wuhan" (hereinafter referred to as "Warning").
这是一本小册子，编印了1000多册，下发至市卫计委机关及委属27家医疗卫生机构。
It is a booklet which has been published in more than 1000 copies and distributed to municipal health and planning authorities and 27 appointed medical and health institutions.
纪委的一篇文章中说，“《警示录》中收录的22件典型案件，是从十八大以来全市卫计系统发生的违纪案件中筛选出来的，涉及人员有单位‘一把手’，也有班子成员、中层干部等，涵盖贪污贿赂、违反八项规定精神以及不作为乱作为等行为。
"The 22 typical cases included in the" Warning "were filtered out of disciplinary cases that have occurred in the city's garrison system since the 18th National Congress, and involved such things as corruption and bribery, violation of the spirit of the eight regulations and acts of omission," said an article by the disciplinary committee
”《警示录》，图片来自武汉纪委官网2019年5月，纪检组又和市卫健委党委联合举办“明法纪知红线”党纪法规知识竞赛，比赛通过斗鱼直播平台进行了全球直播。
The disciplinary team and the municipal health committee jointly held a competition in May 2019 to raise awareness of the "Ming Dynasty Red Line" party discipline laws and regulations, which were broadcast live on a live fish fighting platform.
据“商业人物”不完全统计，在2020年之前的4年里，武汉卫健委有多起通报的违法违规案例。
According to incomplete statistics on "business people," Wuhan Health Commission has reported many violations of the law in the four years to 2020.
2016年，青山区卫计委副主任程明等人违规接受业务往来企业吃请问题。
In 2016, Qingshan District Health and Planning Commission deputy director Cheng Ming and others irregular business transaction enterprise eating problems.
2015年11月29日至12月2日，区卫计委副主任程明、市九医院副院长黄建军、西药房行政副主任谈悦等人赴天津考察期间，四次违规接受业务往来企业的宴请。
From 29 November to 2 December 2015, Deputy Director of District Health and Planning Commission Cheng Ming, Vice President Huang Jianjun of City Jianjun Hospital and Vice-Director of Administration of Western Pharmacy Zhang Yue, among others, visited Tianjin four times during which they illegally accepted banquets from business contacts.
2016年6月7日，青山区纪委给予程明党内严重警告处分；区卫计委给予黄建军行政记过处分；区卫计委党委给予谈悦党内严重警告处分。
On 7 June 2016, the Qingshan District Disciplinary Commission issued a severe warning to Cheng Ming Party; the District Health and Planning Commission issued a disciplinary sanction to Huang Jianjun; and the District Health and Planning Commission issued a severe warning to the Party Committee.
武汉市新洲区卫计委原党委副书记、纪委书记吕明先在2014年至2016年每年春节前后以及本人住院期间，收受下属红十字会医院、妇幼保健院等单位人员送的现金、微信红包、礼品等合计3.54万余元。
Before and after the 2014-2016 Spring Festival and during his hospitalization, Lu Ming, a former deputy party secretary and disciplinary secretary of the Wuhan Xinzhou District Health and Planning Commission, received more than 35,400 yuan in cash, micromail, red envelopes and gifts from staff of the Red Cross and Maternal and Child Health Centres under his command.
新洲区纪委给予吕明先撤销党内职务处分，明确其职务层次由副处级降为正科级。
The discipline committee of Xinzhou District gave Lv Ming the dismissal of party posts and made it clear that his post level was downgraded from deputy to official.
2017年，纪委发现，江夏区卫计系统存在数据弄虚作假，虚报基本公共卫生服务人数、服务次数问题。
In 2017, the disciplinary committee found that the Jiangxia District Wei system data fraud, misrepresentation of the number of basic public health services, the number of services.
江夏区卫计委相关负责人被问责。
Jiang Xia District Health Planning Commission responsible for the accountability.
区卫计委疾控科科长高玉堂行政记过处分、区卫计委副调研员全民生行政警告处分。
District Health and Planning Commission Chief of the CDC Kao Yutang administrative punishment, District Health and Planning Commission deputy investigator Health administrative warning sanctions.
基层医疗机构负有直接责任和领导责任的有关人员也受到了政纪处分和组织处理。
The personnel of the primary medical institutions who have direct responsibility and leading responsibility have also been disciplined and dealt with by administrative discipline and organization.
“这是武汉对形式主义、官僚主义开刀问斩的一个缩影。
"This is Wuhan on the formalism, bureaucracy cut off a miniature.
从去年4月以来，武汉开展不担当、不作为专项治理行动，严查占着位子不作为者。
Since April last year, Wuhan launched no-responsibility, do not act as a special management action, strictly check occupied positions do not act.
”《长江日报》在一篇文章中这么说。
"said the Changjiang Daily in an article.
叁武汉卫健委官网公布了《2018年武汉市卫生健康事业发展简报》。
Wuhan Health Officers' Network published "2018 Wuhan Health Business Development Brief."
简报显示，全市医疗卫生机构总数达6340个，比上年增加269个。
The briefing showed that there were 6,340 medical and health institutions in the city, 269 more than the previous year.
其中医院398个，基层医疗卫生机构5853个，专业公共卫生机构79个。
Of these, 398 were hospitals, 5,853 primary health-care institutions and 79 specialized public health institutions.
与上年相比，医院增加44个。
Compared to the previous year, the number of hospitals increased by 44.
医院按等级分，三级医院61个（其中三级甲等医院27个，含部队医院），二级医院64个，一级医院164个，未定级医院109个。
There are 61 level-III hospitals (27 level-I hospitals, including military hospitals), 64 level-II hospitals, 164 level-I hospitals and 109 ungraded hospitals, by level-III hospital.
医院按床位数分，100~199张医院44个，200~499张床位28个，500~799张医院10个，800张及以上床位34个。
By number of beds in hospitals, there are 44 hospitals, 200-499 beds, 28 hospitals, 500-799 hospitals, and 34 hospitals with 800 beds or more.
专业公共卫生机构中，疾病预防控制中心17个，其中省级1个、市级1个、区级14个，行业属1个。
Of the specialized public health institutions, 17 are disease prevention and control centres, including 1 at the provincial level, 1 at the municipal level, 14 at the district level and 1 in industry.
武汉的医疗实力，全国领先。
Wuhan medical strength, the country's leading.
在正常的环境下，看病可以选择去武汉。
Under normal circumstances, patients can choose to go to Wuhan.
2019年6月，武汉市卫健委公布了2019年重大公共卫生服务专项资金预算。
In June 2019, the Wuhan Health Commission announced the 2019 budget for major public health services.
预算来自财政拨款收入，总额3826.91万元。
The budget came from the financial allocation revenue totalling $38,269,100.
按照《中华人民共和国传染病防治法》《中华人民共和国母婴保健法实施办法》等文件要求，这笔预算主要用于艾滋病、结核病、血吸虫、免疫规划、妇幼保健、孕前优生健康检查等等。
According to the Law of the People's Republic of China on the Prevention and Treatment of Infectious Diseases, the Implementation Measures of the Law of the People's Republic of China on Maternal and Child Health Care, this budget is mainly used for AIDS, tuberculosis, schistosomiasis, immunization programs, maternal and child health check-ups, etc.
武汉市卫健委公布了《2018年武汉市人口老龄化形势分析》，截止2018年末，全市户籍总人口883.73万，其中其中60岁以上老年人187.94万，占总人口的21.27%。
By the end of 2018, the city had 8,837,300 residents, of whom 1,879,400 were over the age of 60, accounting for 21.27 percent of the total population.
图片来自《2018年武汉市人口老龄化形势分析》报告一座正在老龄化的城市。
Pictured here is a report on an aging city from the 2018 Situation Analysis of Population Ageing in Wuhan.
老人多，意味着基础病可能较多，抵抗力比较差。
The number of old people means that basic diseases may be more, less resistance.
